premise_source_doc_sentence: Cited by Vibe Magazine as `` the UK based brand that helped bring trap music to where it is right now '' , All Trap Music has developed from its YouTube roots and now creates and sells compilation albums , hosts international events and sells its own range of merchandise .
Musically , `` Birthday '' combines deep electronic dance beats and police sirens with elements of trap music .
All Trap Music is a music brand founded and curated by Jim Kirk  (  aka JiKay  )  .
Sparse drum beats and vocal chants are woven throughout the song 's composition , which has been described by critics as a mixture of electropunk and EDM , with trap and dubstep elements .
